{"tid":2379044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：封城的結果是促成經濟衰退和物業收購，毫無醫學意義。","createTime":"2021-01-25T03:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T03:42:33.000Z","uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"329fffe49813c3db0b5aa12dd8f4a176bcab1970","tid":2379044,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"陳雲：加州和佛羅里達州採用相反的防疫措施。加州嚴厲封城，佛州生活正常。科學統計結果顯示，加州和佛州的感染率和入院率幾乎一樣，死亡率也是幾乎一樣（佛州還要略低一些）。<br />\n<br />\n封城的結果是促成經濟衰退和物業收購，毫無醫學意義。我一年來已經引述歐美的醫學研究報告斷定，可以在我面書追溯引述的報告和論文。<br />\n<br />\n又真睇彩數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a73a98dcb67b5cde47aaad91e79799ff4cb6de","tid":2379044,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:24:14.000Z","msg":"老師又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04041f38d3b002a326184c9a3bf3c2e889f3a473","tid":2379044,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:25:03.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">扮燒山fans嘅陳雲糞師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱狗孔乙己：戴口罩係恐懼撚、黃絲精神病、助長政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nHardsell支那師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E0f0ybF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE0f0ybF.png&h=927e869b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZwfm41.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZwfm41.png&h=b30cc1de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCJ9rwH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCJ9rwH.png&h=05492094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0vOfJ0.jpg\" data-th